弧长
求曲线y = cosh(2x)/2上从x = 0到x = ln(sqrt(5))那一段的弧长

	弧微分 ds 	= sqrt(dx² + dy²) = sqrt(1 + dy²) dx
	弧长 L 		= ∫(0, ln(sqrt(5))) ds = ∫(0, ln(sqrt(5))) sqrt(1 + dy²) dx

	dy = sinh(2x)
	     L 		= ∫(0, ln(sqrt(5))) sqrt(1 + sinh(2x)²) dx
			= ∫(0, ln(sqrt(5))) cosh(2x) dx
			= (sinh(2x)/2) |(0, ln(sqrt(5)))
			= 1/2 * sinh(2*ln(sqrt(5))) - sinh(0)
			= 1/2 *sinh(ln(5))
			= (e**(ln(5)) - e**(-ln(5)))/4
			= (5 - 1/5)/4
			= 6/5
	     		
